VS Code

Download and install

  1. Navigate to the VS Code download page and download the correct installer
  2. Launch the installer and walk through the steps to install VS Code

Set up in VS Code

  1. Navigate to the VS Code Extension Marketplace and install REditorSupport

  1. Open a new text file
  2. Change the text file language to R in the Select Language Mode menu (control in bottom right) or by clicking on select a language in the text file

  1. VS Code will prompt you to install languageserver; agree to the prompt



Connect to Github

  1. Create a Github account

  2. Connect your Github account to VS Code
